le=\"color: orange;\">行動post啊<br />\n唔好鬆懈啊</span><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gxAcLbL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgxAcLbL.jpg&h=b688acd0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ifkj9Dq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fifkj9Dq.jpg&h=45faad7f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YdmvyvO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYdmvyvO.jpg&h=cb9b01d7&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"8af587f0325640b5d61a5748a95d0cb434b49301","tid":1756710,"uid":93331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T08:26:54.000Z","msg":"無事兒 無事兒<br />\n淘寶送貨姐 別緊張"},{"pid":"779e507667ef2b2b0fcb312f3aea638fc60a25b4","tid":1756710,"uid":196625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T08:27:37.000Z","msg":"nobody cares about cina stop posting."},{"pid":"ad74829b825336de02ff60877dca02928d592051","tid":1756710,"uid":50358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab3f1740ec11ff48225403157efd2d77c0c93f7b","tid":1756710,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T07:05:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/rocket.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F11%2Frocket.jpg&h=706d7b27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n四川西昌衞星發射中心在周六（23日）發射了一枚長征 3B 型火箭，打算將一對北斗衛星送入太空。惟其第一級助推器墮落於一條村莊，砸毀民房，引起大火。據悉，該助推器使用的是聯氨型燃料，毒性較強，不容易撲滅。<br />\n<br />\n美國科技新聞網站《Ars Technica》指中國違反火箭發射規範，沒有選擇在人煙稀少的區域進行發射任務。而類似意外亦非第一次，最嚴重要數在 1996 年，一枚長征 3B 火箭在發射不久就偏離航道撞向一個村莊。中國官方報告有 6 人死於事故，惟外媒推測，至少數百名中國公民在事故中喪生。<br />\n<br />\n美國和其他國家一般將發射站建在沿海地方，但由於中國與蘇聯等鄰近國家的緊張關係，只能在內陸地區建造三個主要的發射中心基地。而當中西昌衞星發射中心附近人口較多，容易受到火箭助推器墮落的影響。惟中國航天科技集團公司（CASC）直至近年才意識到該問題，打算對火箭助推器進行改良，加裝網格式控制翼與噴氣裝置，使助推器在回落時，可以修正方向，選擇安全環境着陸。不過有外媒質疑，網格式控制翼技術是早在西昌衞星發射中心建成前已有的技術，中國早該要進行改良。<br />\n<br />\n就今次意外，據悉並無人命傷亡，而中國相關部門至今尚未有任何回應。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：Ars Technica<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/11/26/chinese-rocket-doused/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F11%2F26%2Fchinese-rocket-doused%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=%2BSgL3cCD37R2%2BMUJ9ALV05gFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=686eb977\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/11/26/chinese-rocket-doused/fun-tech/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T08:29:52.000Z","msg":"大TG"},{"pid":"d745b5476f1afa04bf9a70e0aa244257e680b1b1","tid":1756710,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T08:31:10.000Z","msg":"愛國就預咗為國捐軀㗎啦，唔係剩係掛喺嘴唇邊咁膚淺呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37c7c9210a13483fd099c208cf9923c9a7e4b0fe","tid":1756710,"uid":267331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T08:32:26.000Z","msg":"沒事兒～沒事兒～ 食飯～<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df151e6252f9ed1ced6a72700617346e680f6bd9","tid":1756710,"uid":290883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T08:32:31.000Z","msg":"為國捐驅 係光榮嘅事！！"},{"pid":"65736d4d162cfadff69f1d51e1b29d6082c7a2c1","tid":1756710,"uid":130693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T08:39:49.000Z","msg":"張圖好似舊圖<br />\n印象中依一年內好似爆過一單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c9c0a8c35ceb8431b935f23da4c17b24a78c7c6","tid":1756710,"uid":119082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T08:39:54.000Z","msg":"有毒氣體無害"},{"pid":"720a61e4e18d9179796872f0d9b1f83873dcabea","tid":1756710,"uid":267304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T08:40:05.000Z","msg":"誰家淘寶淘了火箭推進器？貨送來了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcd88a2e6c7c80dec52f63cf46e6bc9d62d9132d","tid":1756710,"uid":184103,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T08:40:33.000Z","msg":"沒事兒 沒事兒 別